customs service the justice department the postal service and 
city officials working with manufacturers and copyright owners 
stephens said a dent was made in illegal trade that takes nearly 
5 million in revenue from city businesses through violation of the 
copyright laws the shirts and other items in the garage would 
bring about 2 million on the street sold over several months he 
estimated 
