copyright protection on lotus development corps 
popular 123 software extends beyond the computer programs 
innerworkings to keyboard commands and onscreen images that 
confront the user a federal judge has ruled 
a spokesman for paperback software international which lost the 
case along with subcontractor stephenson software ltd said the 
company would appeal thursdays decision 
if the decision is upheld in an appeal it will have a 
serious affect on the software business michael burdick 
