with a 11 billion backtaxes bill in the dispute over how the 
company valued oil that it produced in alaska from 1980 to 1983 
the bill consisted of 577 million in taxes plus interest 
this april the company said it was also subject 212 million 
plus interest for 1984 and 1985 
